OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F358A1773349949
OL,3,CNational Grid in #20 million payout
OL,4,Cfor Cumbrian substation failings
OL,6,FThe National Grid has agreed to a #20
OL,7,Fmillion payout to the energy watchdog
OL,8,Ffor failing to properly repair and
OL,9,Fmaintain a substation in Cumbria.
OL,11,FOfgem has said that the National Grid
OL,12,FElectricity Transmission (NGET)
OL,13,Fadmitted breaching the terms of its
OL,14,Flicence at the Harker substation, near
OL,15,FCarlisle, between November 2016 and
OL,16,FNovember 2021.
OL,18,FThe National Grid failed to properly
OL,19,Fmonitor, maintain and repair civil
OL,20,Fassets or to plan and resource
OL,21,Fremediation works.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G1/5
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
