OL,24,ANext Page BBorder NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,359,350,120,260,000,100
PN,35802
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F358A1773349949
OL,3,CNational Grid in #20 million payout
OL,4,Cfor Cumbrian substation failings
OL,6,FA payment will now be made by the
OL,7,FNational Grid into Ofgem's energy
OL,8,Findustry voluntary redress scheme
OL,9,Fwhich supports vulnerable customers.
OL,11,FCathryn Scott, Ofgem's regulatory
OL,12,Fdirector of market oversight and
OL,13,Fenforcement, said: "Delays and asset
OL,14,Ffailures risk reliability issues,
OL,15,Fwhich ultimately impact consumers.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G2/5
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BBorder NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,359,350,120,260,000,100
PN,35803
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F358A1773349949
OL,3,CNational Grid in #20 million payout
OL,4,Cfor Cumbrian substation failings
OL,6,F"This has been a complex and detailed
OL,7,Finvestigation and it was concerning
OL,8,Fthat NGET failed to adequately
OL,9,Fmonitor, maintain and repair some
OL,10,Fcivil assets at Harker substation
OL,11,Fduring the period being investigated.
OL,13,F"It is right that NGET has accepted
OL,14,Fits failings at this substation."
OL,16,FThe National Grid have since carried
OL,17,Fout repairs at Harker.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G3/5
