PN,35804
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F358A1773349949
OL,3,CNational Grid in #20 million payout
OL,4,Cfor Cumbrian substation failings
OL,6,FA National Grid spokesperson said:
OL,7,F"Repairs at the substation and changes
OL,8,Fto how we manage these assets were
OL,9,Fcomplete by 2022.
OL,11,F"A major programme of investment at
OL,12,FHarker began in 2024 to rebuild and
OL,13,Fupgrade the entire site, including
OL,14,Freplacing the existing substations
OL,15,Fwith two new substations adjacent to
OL,16,Fthe current site."
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G4/5
